ADD . /var/app

ARG EXTRA_CONF=
RUN autoreconf -fvi
RUN ./configure --build="$(dpkg-architecture --query DEB_BUILD_GNU_TYPE)" $EXTRA_CONF
RUN make
RUN make check
CMD xvfb-run -a ./src/tym -u ./lua/e2e.lua
